{"title":"Polygonal CSS","link":"https://www.adamkoch.com/2009/03/04/polygonal-css/","pubDate":"Wed, 04 Mar 2009 20:51:24 +0000","dc:creator":"admin","guid":[{"_":"http://www.adamkoch.com/?p=1486","$":{"isPermaLink":"false"}}],"description":[""],"content:encoded":"<a href=\"http://www.zachleat.com/web/\">Zach</a> tweeted about an <a href=\"http://www.filamentgroup.com/lab/image_free_css_tooltip_pointers_a_use_for_polygonal_css/\">article on Polygonal CSS</a> which got me thinking of this one time when I ran across a way to create circles from the &lt;hr&gt; tag. So I whipped up this little demonstration. \r\n\r\nNote: I've testing this in Firefox 3 and IE 7. It works in Firefox, but <em>not</em> in IE. Sorry!\r\n\r\n&lt;hr width=&quot;0&quot; size=&quot;50&quot; noshade=&quot;noshade&quot; /&gt;\r\n<hr width=\"0\" size=\"50\" noshade=\"noshade\" />\r\n\r\n&lt;hr width=&quot;0&quot; size=&quot;100&quot; noshade=&quot;noshade&quot; style=&quot;border: 40px solid red;&quot; /&gt;\r\n<hr width=\"0\" size=\"100\" noshade=\"noshade\" style=\"border: 40px solid red;\" />\r\n\r\n&lt;hr width=&quot;0&quot; size=&quot;100&quot; noshade=&quot;noshade&quot; style=&quot;border-top: 40px solid red; border-bottom: 40px solid red;&quot; /&gt;\r\n<hr width=\"0\" size=\"100\" noshade=\"noshade\" style=\"border-top: 40px solid red; border-bottom: 40px solid red;\" />\r\n\r\n&lt;hr width=&quot;0&quot; size=&quot;50&quot; noshade=&quot;noshade&quot; style=&quot;border-top: 40px solid red; border-bottom: 40px solid red;&quot; /&gt;\r\n<hr width=\"0\" size=\"50\" noshade=\"noshade\" style=\"border-top: 40px solid red; border-bottom: 40px solid red;\" />\r\n\r\n&lt;hr width=&quot;0&quot; size=&quot;100&quot; noshade=&quot;noshade&quot; style=&quot;border-top: 50px solid red; border-bottom: 50px solid red;&quot; /&gt;\r\n<hr width=\"0\" size=\"100\" noshade=\"noshade\" style=\"border-top: 50px solid red; border-bottom: 50px solid red;\" />\r\n\r\n&lt;hr width=&quot;0&quot; size=&quot;100&quot; noshade=&quot;noshade&quot; style=&quot;color: green; border-top: 50px solid red; border-bottom: 50px solid red;; border-right: 50px solid red;&quot; /&gt;\r\n<hr width=\"0\" size=\"100\" noshade=\"noshade\" style=\"color: green; border-top: 50px solid red; border-bottom: 50px solid red;; border-right: 50px solid red;\" />\r\n","excerpt:encoded":"","wp:post_id":"1486","wp:post_date":"2009-03-04 14:51:24","wp:post_date_gmt":"2009-03-04 20:51:24","wp:post_modified":["2009-07-23 23:38:21"],"wp:post_modified_gmt":["2009-07-24 05:38:21"],"wp:comment_status":["open"],"wp:ping_status":["open"],"wp:post_name":"polygonal-css","wp:status":"publish","wp:post_parent":["0"],"wp:menu_order":["0"],"wp:post_type":"post","wp:post_password":[""],"wp:is_sticky":["0"],"category":[{"_":"Professional","$":{"domain":"category","nicename":"professional"}}],"wp:postmeta":[{"wp:meta_key":["aktt_notify_twitter"],"wp:meta_value":["no"]},{"wp:meta_key":["_edit_last"],"wp:meta_value":["1"]},{"wp:meta_key":["_jetpack_related_posts_cache"],"wp:meta_value":["a:1:{s:32:\"37550b67d263a3ce789993dc25046c5f\";a:2:{s:7:\"expires\";i:1627497060;s:7:\"payload\";a:6:{i:0;a:1:{s:2:\"id\";i:1730;}i:1;a:1:{s:2:\"id\";i:1620;}i:2;a:1:{s:2:\"id\";i:1844;}i:3;a:1:{s:2:\"id\";i:1218;}i:4;a:1:{s:2:\"id\";i:1495;}i:5;a:1:{s:2:\"id\";i:2164;}}}}"]}],"tidyCategory":"Professional","tidyTags":[]}

